%         = & (A + B + 2) \sum_{l = 0}^{\lfloor \frac{M - 1}{2} \rfloor} (AB)^{l} - 1 + ((-1)^{M}+1) (AB)^{\lfloor \frac{M}{2} \rfloor}\;.
